Module com.example.gymmembershipgui

Package com.example.gymmembershipgui

package com.example.gymmembershipgui
  • Class
    Description
    ClassSchedule
    Defines a schedule with array of classes and int with num of classes.
    Date
    Date defines a date given a month, day, and year, and checks its validity.
    Family
    Family is defined by a number of guest passes and all Member attributes.
    FitnessClass
    FitnessClass is defined by attendees, instructor, name, time, and location.
    GymManagerController
    GymManagerController manages a member database as well as a class schedule.
    GymManagerMain
    This is the class that runs the GUI for the Gym Membership project.
    Instructors
    Instructor defines the five teachers who teach fitness classes.
    Location
    Location defines five gym locations with their zip code and county.
    Member
    Member defines members given a name, birthday, expiration, and location.
    MemberDatabase
    MemberDatabase manages the members at a gym, or in a fitness class.
    Months
    Months defines each calendar month with its order, abbreviation, and days.
    Premium
    Premium is defined by a number of guest passes and all Member attributes.
    Time
    Time defines the times classes are held: morning, afternoon, and evening.
